data.title: Great Bento  & Sushi
data.text:
Went with family during lunch.  Very busy and slow but worth it.   Tried Teriyaki Chicken Bento, Dragon & Rainbow Roll.   Very tasty & yummy.  Would recommend.  

New in downtown Tracy. 👍🏻

data.title: Replaced Emos, new restaurant!
data.text: Was disappointed that Emos permanently closed but my disappointment soon proved to be short-lived as the replacement Aoyama Sushi is great! Even though I will forever miss Emos kalbi, Aoyama (new owner and menu) has a lot going for it. Service was prompt and upbeat. We ordered Cherry Blossom sushi, kalbi appetizer ($$$), sashimi platter : and all were presented beautifully and tasted fresh. The sushi-chef later came by to check on us and offered free tempura/fried icecream, which everyone enjoyed! Great dinner by Aoyama. For the sushi purist, they seem Korean and not Japanese.
